    <h1 class="page-title">Travelling Course — <em>English B1</em></h1>
    <p class="page-subtitle">From independent traveller to fluent cultural explorer. Handle complex travel situations, tell rich stories, engage with locals on any topic, navigate bureaucracy, and travel entirely in English with confidence and sophistication.</p>
    <div class="level-pill">✈️ Level B1 · 10 units · 50 lessons</div>
  </header>
